    "name": "佣兵猎手",
    "steam_appid": 1843840,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">如需了解更多游戏相关资讯，咨询游戏问题等，欢迎加入官方QQ群：<strong>2151086820</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/4edabe49c8b62726d73d74af333d309c.avif?t=1771328483\" width=1080 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/1e9695d9fc980c8ba6b7fc9b68cdf8e7.poster.avif?t=1771328483\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/1e9695d9fc980c8ba6b7fc9b68cdf8e7.webm?t=1771328483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/1e9695d9fc980c8ba6b7fc9b68cdf8e7.mp4?t=1771328483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地球上最富有的CEO驾鹤西归，留下了商业帝国群雄无首。商战也是战争，需要冲锋陷阵的士兵。而有了MERX应用，每位商人都能买来私人雇佣军，就好像点外卖那样轻松便捷！在一片混乱和争夺中，唯有一支独立的精英小队敢于揭竿反抗，行侠仗义。他们就是——叛警阵地！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战役</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/189aa700c00436213aa9cd1fcf9cbf05.poster.avif?t=1771328483\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/189aa700c00436213aa9cd1fcf9cbf05.webm?t=1771328483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/189aa700c00436213aa9cd1fcf9cbf05.mp4?t=1771328483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投身于一场肾上腺素飙升的战役——火爆的合作枪战与策略规划在此完美融合。组队协作，收集情报，完成目标，在充满变数的任务中浴血奋战。获取技能并升级武器，以对抗“五星佣兵”——这位致命的契约猎手将挑战你团队的极限。。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >极高复玩性</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/9883e6d90f9772a1fb7b33ee85831996.poster.avif?t=1771328483\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/9883e6d90f9772a1fb7b33ee85831996.webm?t=1771328483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/9883e6d90f9772a1fb7b33ee85831996.mp4?t=1771328483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >讲求战略，一路拼杀，在4个不同的地点完成各类任务：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机场</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商场</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >办公室</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >石油钻塔</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每张地图不仅面积广大，而且采用了参数化设计系统，每局游戏都能为你带来新的策略和挑战。玩法不断变化和演进，每个任务都如初见，始终精彩独特，让玩家在每场战役中都能享受不一样的刺激。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI 职业</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你和你团队的战略规划以及战术合作水平如何？就让这群雇佣军来检验吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>士兵</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/d70ae49a322e42f1c3e75de2ca668290.poster.avif?t=1771328483\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/d70ae49a322e42f1c3e75de2ca668290.webm?t=1771328483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/d70ae49a322e42f1c3e75de2ca668290.mp4?t=1771328483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >切勿小觑，士兵是 MERX 小队的中坚力量。士兵们将利用所处环境，并与小队其他单位协同作战，正面挑战叛警精英。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>狂战士</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/f5631b44b733a6e8435dfded4bc7b106.poster.avif?t=1771328483\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/f5631b44b733a6e8435dfded4bc7b106.webm?t=1771328483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/f5631b44b733a6e8435dfded4bc7b106.mp4?t=1771328483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >狂战士是“混乱与浩劫”的代言人，能彻底摧毁你精心制订的战斗计划。他们摄入了各种强化药物和制剂，对自己是死是伤完全不在乎，唯一的目标是近身报私仇，用砍刀把你的整支队伍劈成碎片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>狙击手</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/ce15347c03dd2de0d06b9cf5e4889875.poster.avif?t=1771328483\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/ce15347c03dd2de0d06b9cf5e4889875.webm?t=1771328483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/ce15347c03dd2de0d06b9cf5e4889875.mp4?t=1771328483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >狙击手躲在远处的坚固堡垒中，守护着要害区域，能压制并击退进犯者。要判断战场上是否有狙击手，唯有寻找狙枪的瞄准激光束。不过等你看到激光束，队友有可能已经被爆头了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重装兵</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/c1b80b9789ad45721b02ae44e471b0ad.poster.avif?t=1771328483\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/c1b80b9789ad45721b02ae44e471b0ad.webm?t=1771328483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/c1b80b9789ad45721b02ae44e471b0ad.mp4?t=1771328483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重装兵块头大、行动慢，不过他们不找掩体躲避，敢正面吞子弹。哪怕弹匣打光，你也只能给他们挠个痒痒。面对重装兵，要么转身逃跑，要么动脑筋寻找他们的弱点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>五星佣兵</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MERX 应用中有一群佣兵获得了最高五星评级，他们就是——传奇 MERX 指挥官！对付他们必须谨慎行事，他们对你和你的团队而言极度危险。关于这些 MERX 的情报寥寥无几，不过能确定的是，他们是游戏终局的对手，需要你的战队拼尽所有力量，才有机会将其打败。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >直观易上手的玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏易于上手却难于精通，无论是新手玩家还是资深老手，都能乐在其中。痴迷快节奏的激烈战斗？或是偏爱慢节奏、注重策略与技巧的玩法？游戏为你打开这两种玩法的大门，任玩家选择专属自己的风格。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩转拼杀之财。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在前线赚得收益，然后购买新的装备和硬件，充实、升级自己的军械库。从一支手枪和一件防弹背心开始白手起家，以策略与协作制胜，成功完成一项又一项的任务，最终打造属于自己的精英军械库。通过各种配件和装备升级你的武器装备，在战场上求生。以自己的方式制霸战场。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合作团队玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >携手对抗 MERX 的威胁。游戏的设计核心是团队合作，让玩家们在战斗中通力达成目标。通过打造专属叛警角色，制定策略、灵活应变、战胜逆境。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器和自定义</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赚钱购买武器和装备。你可以购买心仪的全套装备，也可以冒险投入资金，通过“神秘投放”系统获取仅限该系统产出的稀有物品。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 余款武器，每款均有多款皮肤</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40 余款专为你的武器库打造的特制装备与配件</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60 余款外观装饰物品，含多款皮肤</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 个地点，24 种任务布局</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/186a41394e50f6a0acc11e11c4adac7b.poster.avif?t=1771328483\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/186a41394e50f6a0acc11e11c4adac7b.webm?t=1771328483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843840/extras/186a41394e50f6a0acc11e11c4adac7b.mp4?t=1771328483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
